    <div class="cta-box">
      <div>
        <div class="cta-text">Build a Product Management Claude Project that knows your roadmap</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">Treetop helps B2B product teams turn these prompts into a configured Claude Project with your personas, PRD templates, and prioritization framework built in. Start with an AI Audit or go straight to Implementation.</div>
